quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  23,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  23,1,be shak imaan walay raastgar hogaye
  23,2,jo namaz mein ijzo niaz karte hain
  23,3,aur jo behooda baton se munh moray rehtay hain
  23,4,aur jo zakaat ada karte hain
  23,5,aur jo apni sharamgahon ki hifazat karte hain
  23,6,magar apni biwion se ya ( kanizon se ) jo un ki Malik hoti hain ke ( un se ) mubashrat karne se inhen malamat nahi
  23,7,aur jo un ke siwa ouron ke taalib hon woh ( khuda ki muqarrar ki hui hadd se ) nikal jaane walay hain
  23,8,aur jo amanaton aur iqraron ko malhooz rakhtay hain
  23,9,aur jo namazon ki pabandi karte hain
  23,10,yeh hi log meeras haasil karne walay hain
  23,11,( yani ) jo bahisht ki meeras haasil karen ge. aur is mein hamesha rahen ge
  23,12,aur hum ne ensaan ko matti ke khlase se pedakiya hai
  23,13,phir is ko aik mazboot ( aur mehfooz ) jagah mein nutfa bana kar rakha
  23,14,phir nutfay ka lothrha banaya. phir lothary ki booti banai phir booti ki haddiyan banayen phir hadion par gosht ( post ) charhaya. phir is ko nai soorat mein bana diya. to khuda jo sab se behtar bananay wala bara babarkat hai
  23,15,phir is ke baad tum mrjate ho
  23,16,phir qayamat ke roz uttha kharray kiye jao ge
  23,17,aur hum ne tumahray oopar ( ki janib ) saat aasman peda kiye. aur hum khalqat se ghaafil nahi hain
  23,18,aur hum hi ne aasman se aik andazay ke sath pani nazilkiya. phir is ko zameen mein thehra diya aur hum is ke nabood kardainay par bhi Qadir hain
  23,19,"phir hum ne is se tumahray liye khajoron aur angarro ke baagh banaye, un mein tumahray liye bohat se meway peda hotay hain. aur un mein se tum khatay bhi ho"
  23,20,aur woh darakht bhi ( hum hi ne pedakiya ) jo tor seena mein peda hota hai ( yani Zaitoon ka darakht ke ) khanay ke liye roghan aur saalan liye hue aُgta hai
  23,21,aur tumahray liye charpayon mein bhi Ibrat ( aur nishani ) hai ke un ke piton mein hai is se hum tumhe ( doodh ) pilate hain aur tumahray liye un mein aur bhi bohat se faiday hain aur baaz ko tum khatay bhi ho
  23,22,aur un par aur kashtiyon par tum sawaar hotay ho
  23,23,"aur hum ne Nooh ko un ki qoum ki taraf bheja to unhon ne un se kaha ke ae qoum! khuda hi ki ibadat karo is ke siwa tumhara koi mabood nahi,kiya tum drtay nahi"
  23,24,to un ki qoum ke sardar jo kafir they kehnay lagey ke yeh to tum hi jaissa aadmi hai. tum par barayi haasil karni chahta hai. aur agar khuda chahta to farishtay utaar deta. hum ne apne aglay baap dada mein to yeh baat kabhi suni nahi thi
  23,25,is aadmi ko to deewangi ( ka aarzah ) hai to is ke baray mein kuch muddat intzaar karo
  23,26,Nooh ne kaha ke perwar-digaar unhon ne mujhe jhtlaya hai to meri madad kar
  23,27,"pas hum ne un ki taraf wahi bhaije ke hamaray samnay aur hamaray hukum se aik kashti banaao. phir jab hamara hukum aa puhanche aur tanoor ( pani se bhar kar ) josh maarny lagey to sab ( qisam ke hewanat ) mein jora jora ( yani nar aur madah ) do do kashti mein bitha do aur apne ghar walon ko bhi, so un ke jin ki nisbat un mein se ( halaak honay ka ) hukum pehlay sadir hochuka hai. aur zaalmon ke baray mein hum se kuch nah kehna, woh zaroor duubo diye jayen ge"
  23,28,aur jab tum aur tumahray saathi kashti mein baith jao to ( khuda ka shukar karna aur ) kehna ke sab tareef khuda hi ko ( sazawar ) hai. jis ne hum ko nijaat bakhsh zalim logon se
  23,29,aur ( yeh bhi ) dua karna ke ae perwar-digaar hum ko mubarak jagah اتاریو aur to sab se behtar aُtarne wala hai
  23,30,be shak is ( qissay ) mein nishanain hain aur hamein to azmaish karni thi
  23,31,phir un ke baad hum ne aik aur jamaat peda ki
  23,32,"aur un hi mein se un mein aik paighambar bheja ( jis ne un se kaha ) ke khuda hi ki ibadat karo ( ke ) is ke siwa tumhara koi mabood nahi, tokiya tum drtay nahi"
  23,33,"to un ki qoum ke sardar jo kafir they aur akhirat ke anay ko jhoot samajte they aur duniya ki zindagi mein hum ne un ko aasoudgi day rakhi thi. kehnay lagey ke yeh to tum hi jaissa aadmi hai, jis qisam ka khana tum khatay ho, isi terhan ka yeh bhi khata hai aur jo pani tum peetay ho isi qisam ka yeh bhi peeta hai"
  23,34,aur agar tum apne hi jaisay aadmi ka kaha maan liya to ghatay mein par gay
  23,35,kiya yeh tum se yeh kehta hai ke jab tum mar jao ge aur matti ho jao ge aur istikhwan ( ke siwa kuch nah rahay ga ) to tum ( zameen se ) nikalay jao ge
  23,36,jis baat ka tum se wadakiya jata hai ( bohat ) baeed aur ( bohat ) baeed hai
  23,37,"zindagi to yahi hamari duniya ki zindagi hai ke ( isi mein ) hum martay aur jeetay hain, aur hum phir nahi uthaiye jayen ge"
  23,38,yeh to aik aisa aadmi hai jis ne khuda par jhoot iftirakiya hai aur hum is ko maan-ne walay nahi
  23,39,paighambar ne kaha ke ae perwar-digaar unhon ne mujhe jhoota samgha hai to meri madad kar
  23,40,farmaya ke yeh thoray hi arsay mein pasheman ho kar reh jayen ge
  23,41,"to un ko ( wadahbarhaq ke mutabiq ) zor ki aawaz ne aapkrha, to hum ne un ko kora kar daala. pas zalim logon par laanat hai"
  23,42,phir un ke baad hum ne aur jamaten peda kee
  23,43,koi jamaat apne waqt se nah agay ja sakti hai nah peechay reh sakti hai
  23,44,phir hum ne pay darpay apne paighambar bhaijtay rahay. jab kisi aُmt ke paas is ka paighambar aata tha to woh usay jutlatay they to hum bhi baaz ko baaz ke peechay ( halaak karte aur un par azaab ) laatay rahay aur un ke afsaanay banatay rahay. pas jo log imaan nahi laatay un par laanat
  23,45,phir hum ne moose aur un ke bhai Haroon ko apni nishanain aur Daleel zahir day kar bheja
  23,46,"( yani ) firaon aur is ki jamaat ki taraf, to unhon ne taqqaburkiya aur woh sarkash log they"
  23,47,kehnay lagey kekiya hum un apne jaisay do admion par imaan le ayen aur unn ko qoum ke log hamaray khidmat gaar hain
  23,48,to unn logon ne unn ki takzieeb ki so ( aakhir ) halaak kar diye gay
  23,49,aur hum ne moose ko kitaab di thi taakay woh log hadaayat payen
  23,50,"aur hum ne maryam ke betay ( eesa ) aur un ki maa ko ( apni ) nishani banaya tha aur un ko aik onche jagah par jo rehne ke Laiq thi aur jahan ( nthra howa ) pani jari tha, panah di thi"
  23,51,ay peghambroo! pakeeza cheezein khao aur amal naik karo. jo amal tum karte ho mein un se waaqif hon
  23,52,aur yeh tumhari jamaat ( haqeeqat mein ) aik hi jamaat hai aur mein tumhara perwar-digaar hon to mujh se daro
  23,53,to phir aapas mein apne kaam ko mutafarraq karkay judda judda kardiya. jo cheezein jis firqay ke paas hai woh is se khush ho raha hai
  23,54,to un ko aik muddat taq un ki ghaflat mein rehne do
  23,55,kiya yeh log khayaal karte hain ke hum jo duniya mein un ko maal aur beton se madad dete hain
  23,56,to ( is se ) un ki bhalai mein jaldi kar rahay hain ( nahi ) balkay yeh samajte hi nahi
  23,57,jo apne perwar-digaar ke khauf se drtay hain
  23,58,aur jo apne perwar-digaar ki ayaton par imaan rakhtay hain
  23,59,aur jo apne perwar-digaar ke sath shareek nahi karte
  23,60,aur jo day satke hain dete hain aur un ke dil is baat se drtay rehtay hain ke un ko apne perwar-digaar ki lout kar jana hai
  23,61,yahi log nakiyon mein jaldi kere aur yahi unn ke liye agay nikal jatay hain
  23,62,aur hum kisi shakhs ko is ki taaqat se ziyada takleef nahi dete aur hamaray paas kitaab hai jo sach sach keh deti hai aur un logon par zulm nahikiya jaye ga
  23,63,"magar un ke dil un ( baton ) ki taraf se ghaflat mein ( parre hue ) hain, aur un ke siwa aur aamaal bhi hain jo yeh karte rehtay hain"
  23,64,yahan taq ke jab hum ne un mein se aasooda haal logon ko pakar liya to woh is waqt chalayein ge
  23,65,aaj mat chalao! tum ko hum se kuch madad nahi miley gi
  23,66,meri ayatain tum ko parh parh kar sunai jati theen aur tum ultay paon phir phir jatay they
  23,67,"un se sar kashi karte, kahaaniyon mein mashgool hotay aur behooda bakwaas karte they"
  23,68,kiya unhon ne is kalaam mein ghhor nahikiya ya un ke paas koi aisi cheez aayi hai jo un ke aglay baap dada ke paas nahi thi
  23,69,"ya yeh apne paighambar ko jantay pehjantay nahi, is wajah se un ko nahi mantay"
  23,70,kiya yeh kehte hain ke usay soda hai ( nahi ) balkay woh un ke paas haq ko le kar aeye hain aur un mein se aksar haq ko napasand karte hain
  23,71,aur khuday-e ( barhaq ) un ki khawahishon par chalay to aasman aur zameen aur jo un mein hain sab darham barham ho jaien. balkay hum ne un ke paas un ki nasiyaat ( ki kitaab ) pouncha di hai aur woh apni ( kitaab ) nasiyaat se munh phair rahay hain
  23,72,"kiya tum un se ( tableegh ke siilay mein ) kuch maal mangte ho, to tumhara perwar-digaar ka maal bohat acha hai aur woh sab se behtar rizaq dainay wala hai"
  23,73,aur tum to un ko seedhay rastay ki taraf bulatay ho
  23,74,aur jo log akhirat par imaan nahi laatay woh raste se allag ho rahay hain
  23,75,"aur agar hum un par reham karen aur jo takleifein un ko poanch rahi hain, woh daur kar dein to apni sar kashi par uray rahen ( aur ) bhataktay ( phrin )"
  23,76,aur hum ne un ko azaab mein pakra to bhi unhon ne khuda ke agay aajzi nah ki aur woh aajzi karte hi nahi
  23,77,yahan taq ke jab hum ne par azaab shadeed ka darwaaza khol diya to is waqt wahan na umeed hogaye
  23,78,aur wohi to hai jis ne tumahray kaan aur ankhen aur dil banaye. ( lekin ) tum kam shkrgzari karte ho
  23,79,aur wohi to hai jis ne tum ko zameen mein pedakiya aur isi ki taraf tum jama ho kar jao ge
  23,80,"aur wohi hai jo zindagi bakhshta hai aur mout deta hai aur raat aur din ka bdalty rehna isi ka tasarruf hai,kiya tum samajte nahi"
  23,81,baat yeh hai ke jo baat aglay ( kafir ) kehte they isi terhan ki ( baat yeh ) kehte hain
  23,82,kehte hain ke jab hum mar jayen ge aur matti ho jayen ge aur istikhwan ( boseedah ke siwa kuch ) nah rahay ga tokiya hum phir uthaye jayen ge ?
  23,83,yeh wada hum se aur hum se pehlay hamaray baap dada se bhi hota chala aaya hai ( aji ) yeh to sirf aglay logon ki kahaniyan hain
  23,84,kaho ke agar tum jantay ho to batao ke zameen aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab kis ka maal hai ?
  23,85,jhat bol utheen ge ke khuda ka. kaho ke phir tum sochte kyun nahi ?
  23,86,( un se ) pucho ke saat asmano ka kon maalik hai aur arsh azeem ka ( kon ) maalik ( hai? )
  23,87,"be sakhta keh den ge ke yeh ( cheezein ) khuda hi ki hain, kaho ke phir tum drtay kyun nahi ?"
  23,88,kaho ke agar tum jantay ho to batao ke woh kon hai jis ke haath mein har cheez ki badshahi hai aur woh panah deta hai aur is ke maqabil koi kisi ko panah nahi day sakta
  23,89,"foran keh den ge ke ( aisi badshahi to ) khuda hi ki hai, to kaho phir tum par jaadoo kahan se par jata hai ?"
  23,90,baat yeh hai ke hum ne un ke paas haq pouncha diya hai aur jo ( buut parasti kiye jatay hain ) be shak jhutay hain
  23,91,"khuda ne nah to ( apna ) kisi ko beta banaya hai aur nah is ke sath koi mabood hai, aisa hota to har mabood apni apni makhloqaat ko le kar chal deta aur aik dosray par ghalib ajata. yeh log jo kuch khuda ke baray mein bayan karte hain khuda is se pak hai"
  23,92,woh posheeda aur zahir ko jaanta hai aur ( mushriq ) jo is ke sath shareek karte hain is ki shaan is se onche hai
  23,93,"( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) kaho ke ae perwar-digaar jis azaab ka un ( kufar ) se wada ho raha hai, agar to meri zindagi mein un par nazil karkay mujhe bhi dikhade"
  23,94,to ae perwar-digaar mujhe ( is se mehfooz rkhiye aur ) un zaalmon mein shaamil nah kijiye
  23,95,aur jo wada hum un se kar rahay hain hum tum ko dikha kar un par nazil karne par Qadir hain
  23,96,aur buri baat ke jawab mein aisi baat kaho jo nihayat achi ho. aur yeh jo kuch bayan karte hain hamein khoob maloom hai
  23,97,aur kaho ke ae perwar-digaar! mein shaitano ke waswason se teri panah mangta ho
  23,98,aur ae perwar-digaar! is se bhi teri panah mangta hon ke woh mere paas آaa maujood hon
  23,99,( yeh log isi terhan ghaflat mein rahen ge ) yahan taq ke jab un mein se kisi ke paas mout aajay gi to kahe ga ke ae perwar-digaar! mujhe phir ( duniya mein ) wapas bhaij day
  23,100,"taakay mein is mein jisay chore aaya hon naik kaamkiya karoon. hargiz nahi. yeh aik aisi baat hai ke woh usay zabaan se keh raha hoga ( aur is ke sath amal nahi hoga ) aur is ke peechay barzakh hai ( jahan woh ) is din taq ke ( dobarah ) uthaye jayen ge, ( rahen ge )"
  23,101,phir jab sor phonka jaye ga to nah to un mein qrabtain hon gi aur nah aik dosray ko poucheen ge
  23,102,to jin ke ( amlon ke ) boojh bhaari hon ge. woh Falah panay walay hain
  23,103,"aur jin ke boojh halkay hon ge woh log hain jinhon ne apne tain khasaray mein dala, hamesha dozakh mein rahen ge"
  23,104,aag un ke monhon ko jhulas day gi aur woh is mein teori charhaye hon ge
  23,105,kiya tum ko meri ayatain parh kar nahi sunai jatein theen ( nahi ) tum un ko suntay they ( aur ) jutlatay they
  23,106,ae hamaray perwar-digaar! hum par hamari kam bakhti ghalib hogayi aur hum raste se bhatak gay
  23,107,"ae perwar-digaar! hum ko is mein se nikaal day, agar hum phir ( aisay kaam ) karen to zalim hon ge"
  23,108,( khuda ) farmaiye ga ke isi mein zillat ke sath parre raho aur mujh se baat nah karo
  23,109,mere bundon mein aik giroh tha jo duakiya karta tha ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar hum imaan laaye to too hum ko bakhash day aur hum par reham kar aur to sab se behtar reham karne wala hai
  23,110,to tum un se tamaskhur karte rahay yahan taq ke un ke peechay meri yaad bhi bhool gay aur tum ( hamesha ) un se hansikiya karte they
  23,111,"aaj mein ne unn ko unn ke sabr ka badla diya, ke woh kamyaab hogaye"
  23,112,( khuda ) pouchye ga ke tum zameen mein kitney baras rahay ?
  23,113,"woh kahin ge ke hum aik roz ya aik roz se bhi kam rahay they, shumaar karne walon se pooch lijiye"
  23,114,( khuda ) farmaiye ga ke ( wahan ) tum ( bohat hi ) kam rahay. kash tum jantay hotay
  23,115,kiya tum yeh khayaal karte ho ke hum ne tum ko be faida pedakiya hai aur yeh tum hamari taraf lout kar nahi aao ge ?
  23,116,"to khuda jo sacha badshah hai ( is ki shaan ) is se onche hai, is ke siwa koi mabood nahi, wohi arsh buzurag ka maalik hai"
  23,117,aur jo shakhs khuda ke sath aur mabood ko pukaarta hai jis ki is ke paas kuch bhi sanad nahi to is ka hisaab khuda hi ke haan hoga. kuch shak nahi ke kafir rstgari nahi payen ge
  23,118,aur khuda se dua karo ke mere perwar-digaar mujhe bakhash day aur ( mujh par ) reham kar aur to sab se behtar reham karne wala hai
